title: New House, New Car, New Us!
itunes:title: New House, New Car, New Us!
description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Leisha catches Kate up on her Sunday Scaries fighting off hives triggered by an unknown pest. Kate finally skateboards with her dog on a beautiful flat surface in her new neighborhood. And Leisha finally joins the modern world with her new car which she’ll drive to set for the new season of The L Word!
